EV CHARGING NETWORK - MARKET ENTRY ANALYSIS

CLIENT PROBLEM:
- Need to expand EV charging infrastructure across India
- Don't know which cities to target
- Don't know optimal station locations
- Uncertainty on ROI & payback

OUR SOLUTION:
- Data-driven market analysis
- City prioritization model
- Station placement optimization
- 3-year financial projections

RESULTS:
- ₹150Cr opportunity identified
- Top 10 cities ranked by revenue potential
- 156 recommended stations
- 3.2x ROI, 24-month payback

METHODOLOGY:
- Market sizing: EV registrations × daily usage × tariff
- City scoring: 4 factor model (growth, gap, density, subsidies)
- GIS analysis: Optimal location clustering
- Scenario modeling: Conservative/base/optimistic cases

DELIVERABLES:
✓ Interactive Streamlit dashboard
✓ City ranking analysis (CSV downloadable)
✓ Financial projections (Excel models)
✓ Risk assessment & mitigation
✓ Implementation roadmap
